    <patterns>
      <pattern>SemanticSearchService hybrid search: `searchService.SearchAsync(query, indexName: "playbook-embeddings", filter: $"recordType eq '{context.RecordType}'", top: 5)` — follow existing search patterns</pattern>
      <pattern>Fast LLM call for parameter extraction: use a compact system prompt with the candidate list embedded as JSON, ask for structured JSON output; set MaxTokens=200 for fast response</pattern>
      <pattern>Confidence threshold for Stage 2 skip: score &gt;= 0.85 with single candidate → direct match; avoids LLM call for high-confidence single matches</pattern>
